{
  "stem": "5430.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we used to-- in the summer, we used to see the sun settling down and-- or rising in one place, and settling down just a few feet further 20 hours later, in the same spot.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They call these northern summers or whatever-- Northern Lights.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In any case, my father got sick in the forest also, and they let him come back to work in the kitchen sort of on a limited basis.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that too helped us to sustain a little bit, because he would be able to give us a little more proportion and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that lasted until the Nazis invaded Russia, which was in 1941, towards the end of the summer, I believe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeah, it must have been towards the end, because we were there all summer long.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so they-- the Polish government in Russia decided to form a Polish brigade, the Kosciuszko Brigade-- Kosciuszko Brigade.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And because of that, they decided all Polish citizens are no longer enemies of the state and can be released from Siberia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We found out afterwards that the whole Polish brigade, the Kosciuszko Brigade, was sent to the German front, and they were decimated right away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They-- they-- a lot of them died on that-- on that front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not only from camp, all the Polish-- because there were a lot of Polish communists that lived in Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they formed that Polish brigade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And therefore, they decided to release us from Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they permitted us to travel from Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave special permits of propusks, as they call it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How do they spell it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "P-R-O-P-U-S-K.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Propusk.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a permit to travel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you can't travel-- or you couldn't travel in Russia anywhere without a permit, from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
